data.title: Jennie Lee - Biography | San Francisco
data.meta_description: Jennie Lee is a Labor and Employment attorney in San Francisco. She represents employers in state and federal court and before administrative agencies in a broad range of employment matters.
data.meta_site_name: Allen Matkins  - Jennie Lee - Biography | San Francisco
data.text:
Jennie also represents employers in corporate immigration matters. She has extensive experience in obtaining non-immigrant work visas, such as H-1B and L-1 visas, and employment-based immigrant visas for management, professional, and specialized skill employees. She also represents clients in U.S. Department of Labor audits and immigration-related litigation.

Prior to returning to Allen Matkins, Jennie spent two years as in-house employment and labor counsel at Pacific Gas and Electric Company where she was lead attorney in numerous labor arbitrations and employment litigation matters.
